%N A397156 Decimal expansion of the volume of a canonical (dual-uniform) tetragonal trapezohedron with unit short edge length.
%C A397156 The tetragonal trapezohedron is the dual polyhedron of the square antiprism.
%H A397156 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A397156/b397156.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%H A397156 David I. McCooey, <a href="https://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/TetragonalTrapezohedron.html">Tetragonal Trapezohedron</a>.
