%H A397156 <a href="/index/Al#algebraic_04">Index entries for algebraic numbers, degree 4</a>.
%F A397156 Equals sqrt(58 + 41*sqrt(2))/3 = sqrt(58 + 41*A002193)/3.
%F A397156 Equals the largest root of 81*x^4 - 1044*x^2 + 2.
